question: Give me the science labs and art studios that have computers.
sql_query1:
SELECT Learning_Spaces.Name 
FROM Learning_Spaces
WHERE (Learning_Spaces.Type = "Science Lab" OR Learning_Spaces.Type = "Art Studio") AND Learning_Spaces.AvailableResources = "Computers"
sql_query2:
SELECT Learning_Spaces.Name 
FROM Learning_Spaces
WHERE Learning_Spaces.Type = "Science Lab" OR Learning_Spaces.Type = "Art Studio" AND Learning_Spaces.AvailableResources = "Computers"
interpretation1: What science labs have computers and what art studios have the same resource?
interpretation2: List all science labs and also list art studios that have computers.
